        "heading_TGHNNy": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<h2><strong>Refrigeration: Engineered to Preserve, Designed to Impress</strong></h2>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_Tgm7iC": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Choosing the right fridge is one of the most important decisions in designing a functional kitchen. At Cook & Bathe, our refrigeration collection is designed to meet a broad range of lifestyle needs, spatial requirements, and design preferences. Whether you’re upgrading your primary fridge or adding a secondary unit to your home bar or wine cellar, our selection offers tailored solutions that combine energy efficiency, smart storage, and refined finishes.</p><p>Our <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/fridges\">Fridges collection</a> includes a broad spectrum of sizes and configurations, ensuring there’s an option suited to every kitchen—from compact apartments to large family homes. Each model is built with modern refrigeration technology to maintain consistent temperatures, reduce frost build-up, and support food longevity. Whether you’re after spacious internal layouts, adjustable shelving, or dedicated humidity-controlled compartments, you’ll find a fridge designed to enhance both form and function.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
