    "multicolumn_RN4nb9": {
      "type": "multicolumn",
      "blocks": {
        "column_tKKNd8": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/icon_fridge.svg",
            "title": "Freestanding Fridges",
            "text": "<p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/freestanding-fridges\">Freestanding fridges</a> are a popular choice for homeowners who value flexibility and ease of installation. Available in a variety of heights, widths, and capacities, these models allow you to place your fridge wherever suits your kitchen layout. Many include split configurations such as top or bottom-mounted freezers, side-by-side doors, or French-door designs. Freestanding units offer accessibility and storage versatility, with features like reversible doors, LED lighting, and spacious crispers to accommodate large grocery hauls or growing families.</p>",
            "link_label": "Shop Now",
            "link": "shopify://collections/freestanding-fridges"
          }
        },
        "column_zV8BR3": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/icon_fridge.svg",
            "title": "Integrated Fridges",
            "text": "<p>If you’re after a clean, seamless kitchen aesthetic, our <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/integrated-fridges\">integrated fridges</a> are engineered to blend into your cabinetry. These models are ideal for modern, minimalist kitchen designs, allowing you to maintain visual consistency across cupboards and panels. Integrated fridges are available in multiple sizes and are designed with flush-fit doors and concealed ventilation, making them a preferred choice for luxury renovations and premium kitchen builds.</p>",
            "link_label": "Shop Now",
            "link": "shopify://collections/integrated-fridges"
          }
        },
        "column_X346kn": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/icon_barfridges.png",
            "title": "Bar Fridges",
            "text": "<p>Our range of <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/bar-fridges\">bar fridges</a> offers compact convenience for secondary storage. These units are ideal for guest areas, entertainment spaces, office kitchens, or apartment living. Despite their size, bar fridges can include dedicated compartments for cans and bottles, adjustable shelves, and internal lighting. They’re perfect for storing beverages, snacks, or overflow items without taking up the space of a full-sized appliance.</p>",
            "link_label": "Shop Now",
            "link": "shopify://collections/bar-fridges"
          }
        }
      },
