    "rich_text_MaTWry": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_hDJLan": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<h2><strong>Rangehoods: Style That Clears the Air</strong></h2>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_ifrdDc": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>A high-quality rangehood is essential for maintaining clean air, reducing lingering odours, and protecting your kitchen cabinetry from excess moisture and grease. At Cook & Bathe, our <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/rangehoods\">Rangehoods collection</a> offers solutions tailored to a wide range of kitchen layouts, cooking styles, and aesthetic preferences.</p><p>Whether you need a bold feature piece or a subtle design that disappears into your cabinetry, our collection is built around performance, durability, and style. Each model is engineered for powerful extraction, low noise levels, and easy maintenance—giving you a kitchen that not only looks better, but functions better too.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_hDJLan",
        "text_ifrdDc"
      ],
