    "rich_text_TLdbgj": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_j3fLqQ": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>A dependable rangehood is essential for a cleaner, more comfortable kitchen environment. Whether you’re cooking daily meals or preparing larger feasts, proper ventilation helps reduce steam, smoke, and odours while protecting your cabinetry from grease build-up. The <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/rangehoods\">Rangehoods collection</a> at Cook & Bathe includes options for various kitchen layouts and cabinetry styles, so you can choose a model that fits your space and functional needs.</p><p>Each rangehood in our selection is chosen for its performance, durability, and integration potential—supporting both traditional and contemporary kitchens with effective airflow management.</p><h3><strong>Wall Canopy Rangehoods</strong></h3><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/wall-canopy-rangehoods\">Wall Canopy Rangehoods</a> are mounted directly to the wall above your cooktop and offer a prominent visual presence in the kitchen. These models are suitable for a range of kitchen designs and provide strong air extraction performance with simple, easy-to-access operation.</p><p>Available in a variety of widths and finishes, they suit standard cooking configurations and are a reliable choice for effective kitchen ventilation.</p><h3><strong>Undermount Rangehoods</strong></h3><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/undermount-rangehoods\">Undermount Rangehoods</a> are designed to be built into your cabinetry, allowing for a clean, minimalist appearance. They are especially well-suited to kitchens with a focus on seamless design, providing ventilation while remaining discreet. These units integrate neatly into overhead cupboards and help maintain consistent airflow without disrupting the kitchen’s visual layout.</p><h3><strong>Cassette Rangehoods</strong></h3><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/cassette-rangehoods\"> Cassette Rangehoods</a> offer a streamlined solution for those looking to maintain an open or integrated kitchen design. Built to sit flush with the ceiling or overhead cabinetry, cassette rangehoods are an alternative for specific kitchen configurations where traditional wall-mounted or undermount units are not suitable.</p><p>They offer essential ventilation performance while preserving overhead space, contributing to a modern and uncluttered kitchen finish.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
